{"TopicId":196345,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to solve this very weird base problem.","CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T19:25:01Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T19:25:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I thought I would built a base for my kerbals to have vacation. But I had a problem that I never thought of before. Unless your destination is Gilly! My base won\u0027t stay on the ground! The mining drills stop every time the base decides to go for a hop. I have \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrusters on my base, but keeping them on all the time isn\u0027t gonna work. Any ideas?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T19:39:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223839303\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597605901\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204905\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cant think of a username\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, Cant think of a username said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I thought I would built a base for my kerbals to have vacation. But I had a problem that I never thought of before. Unless your destination is Gilly! My base won\u0027t stay on the ground! The mining drills stop every time the base decides to go for a hop. I have \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrusters on my base, but keeping them on all the time isn\u0027t gonna work. Any ideas?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre the drills very close\u00A0to the ground?You should put them as high you can so only their tip reaches underground/ground.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also use structural panels and even grip pads instead of landing legs\u00A0to keep your base kinda less jumpy and drifty in low grav planets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you post a picture of it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-16T19:41:00Z\u0022 title=\u002208/16/2020 07:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 16, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Boyster\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T19:42:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223839311\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597606786\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179192\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Boyster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Boyster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre the drills very close\u00A0to the ground?You should put them as high you can so only their tip reaches underground/ground.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also use structural panels and even grip pads to keep your base kinda less jumpy and drifty in low grav planets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you post a picture of it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe drills don\u0027t have an impact box. Also, are grip pads suppose to stop sliding? my base is going up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T19:43:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223839312\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597606935\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204905\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cant think of a username\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Cant think of a username said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe drills don\u0027t have an impact box. Also, are grip pads suppose to stop sliding? my base is going up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you put the drills very close to the ground when you extend them/use them they lift up your base\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-16T19:44:06Z\u0022 title=\u002208/16/2020 07:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 16, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Boyster\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T19:51:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223839313\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597606983\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179192\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Boyster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Boyster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you put the drills very close to the ground when you extend them/use them they lift up your base\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I extend the drills, the base is ok, but it just wonders upwards randomly at a random time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-16T19:51:53Z\u0022 title=\u002208/16/2020 07:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 16, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Cant think of a username\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T19:58:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223839317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597607512\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204905\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cant think of a username\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Cant think of a username said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I extend the drills, the base is ok, but it just wonders upwards randomly at a random time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmmm, well, you probably already know this but you can activate the drills and the resource thing and go to tracking station or to a different location/vessel and time warp there to produce.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf 