eatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T20:08:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223839325\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597608340\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204905\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cant think of a username\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Cant think of a username said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t get a screenshot now because I am on a different computer, so...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts ok post when/if you can,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E in low grav planets for bases isnt gonna help, most likely will create more problems,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalso if you have strong \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E maybe you should turn some off, or even toggle \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E entirely,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndoes the base lift up only when you use the drills?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T20:13:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, I floats every once in a while. Even without the drills. I visit it often when I go to Eve, and almost every time it was floating.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-16T20:17:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223839331\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597608807\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204905\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cant think of a username\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Cant think of a username said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, I floats every once in a while. Even without the drills. I visit it often when I go to Eve, and almost every time it was floating.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm well, structure panels and grip pads might help....there is also this mod...but its outdated, some claim it still works, no idea\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBack then it was an amazing mod that prevented the bouncing issue....but you know use it with caution, its outdated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022167015\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4461400832\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/169206-131-18x-worldstabilizer-bugfix-for-vessels-bouncing-on-scene-load/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:213px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}